    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>To make or become dark in shade, value, or color; a form of discoloration: the blackening or browning of materials due to such causes as chemical process, exposure to light, the passage of  time.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
